column2: select floor ((p.petroMag_r - # - # * log1# (dbo.fCosmoDl (s.z) ) - p.extinction_r) *#) /#, count (*) from SpecObj s inner join PhotoObj p on s.bestObjID = p.ObjID where s.z > # and s.z < # and p.petroMag_r - # - # * log1# (dbo.fCosmoDl (s.z) ) - p.extinction_r > # and p.petroMag_r - # - # * log1# (dbo.fCosmoDl (s.z) ) - p.extinction_r < # group by floor ((p.petroMag_r - # - # * log1# (dbo.fCosmoDl (s.z) ) - p.extinction_r) *#) order by #
